<note n="0887001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0887001">〔唐〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0887002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0887002">〔等〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0887003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0887003">詔＝勅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
